Get the details of the application with the specified listing ID.<div class=&quot;examples&quot;><p>The following example returns details of an application listing by submitting a GET request on the REST resource using cURL.</p>
<h3>cURL Example</h3>
<pre>
curl -X GET -H &quot;X-Oracle-UserId: <i>partner-email</i>&quot; -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer <i>Access-token</i>&quot; &quot;https://ocm-apis.cloud.oracle.com/appstore/publisher/v1/applications/2801500&quot;
