Get a list of leads for the partner.<div class=&quot;examples&quot;><p>The following example gets leads for a partner, by submitting a GET request on the REST resource using cURL.</p>
<h3>Query Paramters</h3>
<pre>
 1. createdOnRangeStart: YYYY-MM-DD
 2. createdOnRangeEnd: YYYY-MM-DD
 3. orderby: NAME, COMPANY, LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, CREATION_DATE
 4. sortorder: ASC, DESC
</pre>
<h3>cURL Example</h3>
<pre>
curl -X GET -H &quot;X-Oracle-UserId: <i>partner-email</i>&quot; -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer <i>Access-token</i>&quot; &quot;https://ocm-apis.cloud.oracle.com/appstore/publisher/v1/leads?createdonrangestart=2016-01-01&amp;createdonrangeend=2016-05-01&amp;orderby=name&amp;sortorder=ASC&quot;
</pre> 
<h3>Request Header</h3>
<pre>
X-Oracle-UserId: fname.lname@oracle.com 
Authorization: Bearer Access-token 
</pre>
<h3>Request Body</h3>
<pre>
None
</pre> 
<h3>HTTP Status Code:</h3>
<pre>200 OK</pre>
<h3>JSON Response:</h3>
<pre>
