Defaults API returns the default Maps and Filters that can to be applied during search,Search & Export and Search & Match

<p>Versions Supported</p>
<pre>v2,v3,v4</pre>
<div class=&quot;examples&quot;>
<p>Example requests:</p>

<pre>
  /v2/admin/defaults
  /v3/admin/defaults
  /v4/admin/defaults

 </pre>
<p>Example Response:</p>
<pre>
 {
     &quot;defaultFilters&quot;: [
         {
             &quot;filterName&quot;: &quot;CompanyInBusiness&quot;,
             &quot;filterValue&quot;:&quot;Y&quot;
         },
         {
             &quot;filterName&quot;: &quot;Enterprise Companies&quot;,
             &quot;filterValue&quot;:&quot;Y&quot;
         },
         {
         		&quot;filterName&quot;: &quot;Defunct Companies&quot;,
